COPY OF Orangutan tenderly kisses pregnant woman's baby bump Watch | Orangutan tenderly kisses pregnant woman's baby bump 00:31 Telegraph Video , video source Jukin 6 January 2017 â€¢ 7:00am 
A n expectant mother is moved to tears after an orangutan sweetly kisses her baby bump through the glass at Colchester Zoo in Essex. 
48-year-old primate Rajang was filmed leaning forward, trying to kiss and stroke her pregnant belly.
